name: watching too much west world
description:
digital version of a analogical acrylic on canson a3 paper with watercolor application.

part of my study with collage in 2021.
2/3.

i started to mix the materials and think about nowadays, watching west world. what reality, our dreams and fantasies became with the pandemic changes in everybody's life .

this one looks very juvenile from me but it was like was killing part of my bad fantasies with men at that time. 

i will keep one token to sell it with the real collage one day.
hope you like it. 

jomi.
